Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.67,0:00:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't take a detour here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.72,0:00:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just go home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.77,0:00:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If only that rug were still okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Save me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"The monster inside me\Nis about to burst out!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two individuals within Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what you're saying is…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When you stopped by the warehouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that Asian guy and the arsonist\Nwere already in a scuffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the Asian guy\Nnoticed you were there and ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right, Ms. Anna Liebert?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the culprit is\Na member of the far-right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and has turned himself in, saying\Nthe flames were for a festival of race.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your personal references hold up,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so we can stop for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean I can go home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, the people of that district
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,called that Asian\Nby the name of Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Given her outfit, maybe she was trying to\Nengage in prostitution in that district.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, people from the Turkish District\Ncalled the Asian man by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But when we began investigations\Nand said he was a suspected serial killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,they all would say the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd say, "I don't know this man."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I acted as your guarantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Rosso.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been well, Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You disappeared so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done changing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that kind of outfit\Nlooks better on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That look before didn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come. I bet you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not eating, Mr. Rosso?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I ate before I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have a coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like always,\Nyou put in five spoonfuls of sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Coffee doesn't taste good\Nunless it's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to interview for a job,\Nyet your face looked so gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it so strange to put in a lot of sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna, um…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Anna Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I, um…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hired, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a no-brainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If a beauty like you works here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,our business will boom like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You should smile a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your beauty will go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to strain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're an Italian restaurant\Nin a rural town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping busy won't amount to much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Go around the counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring out the food here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll take it to the customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Used plates are placed\Non the right side of the counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wine goes here,\Nand glasses are on this shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's wine above the counter too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tickets with people's orders go here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's wine above the counter,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and glasses are there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nice to meet you"? Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't possibly be\Nthe waitress at a place like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "a place like this"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna is, without a doubt,\Na waitress here starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't that something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna, can I have a carbonara?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna, I'll have a bolognese.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna, can you come and pour me some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one carbonara and a bolognese.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's vongole and rigatoni.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fettuccine is ready too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rosso.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you snatch this cute girl from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say "snatch,"\Nor people will get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to\Na much nicer restaurant than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How's tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.76,0:09:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Lay a hand on our star\Nand you won't get off easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that crybaby Rosso\Nis acting pretty valiant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna, that guy was crying the other day\Nwhile watching a movie on TV at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Another order for squid ink risotto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, they're showing Summertime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The old cinema is showing Summertime, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankfurt has so many movie theaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was on TV the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a real tearjerker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you watched it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The film takes place in\Nthe Italian city of Venice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Venice is a port city from medieval times
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and is called the City of Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The city was originally built on a lagoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why a canal runs through the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to\Nshow you Venice sometime, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been there before, Mr. Rosso?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The music in that film is great too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you've probably heard\Nthe theme song of the movie before too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we go see it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we can still get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd get out late if we see it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for taking the afternoon off\Nfrom the restaurant every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not much going on\Nat this hour anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean to pry…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but where are you going every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, forget I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're free to use\Nyour free time as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shooting practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shooting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, at Mr. Wenkel's shooting range.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you go to Wenkel's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever fired\Na gun before, Mr. Rosso?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A gun? Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just looking at one\Nmakes me tremble in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how it is this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it a taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it taste like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's garlic, olive oil, parsley, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't taste\Nthe other ingredients, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's not real pasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything comes with training.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Rosso, you can take a bath now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe such a film\Nexisted when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Rosso, you always cried\Nas you watched films.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:16:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no time to watch them\Nwhen I was young, even if I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I ate so many delicious foods back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.01,0:16:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't remember\Nthe taste of a single dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even know the taste of sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The taste of sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You know about me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,After you left, I looked into you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You went missing after your parents\Nwere killed by an unknown individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have a job for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want me to teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about having you teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a professor researching you\Nat my university's law school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ristorante Nino incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sacco Milano incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mr. Sabatini bomb murder incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Each case was a murder\Nconducted through different means,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and he was called as a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But they all lacked sufficient evidence\Nand led to no charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that professor\Nthought of an interesting theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on that theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you were undoubtedly\Na professional hit man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And an elite one at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people do you think I've killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest,\NI don't even remember myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was when I was still a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it,\NI had joined an organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stealing. Blackmail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the end, I became a hit man,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,since I'd get to eat good food\Nas a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was working.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.97,0:18:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just like any other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a café in broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This stranger from who knows where\Nwas my next hit out of countless others,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and I aimed my gun at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That stranger had ordered a coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, he started putting in sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,One spoonful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Two spoonfuls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Three spoonfuls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Four spoonfuls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When he put in\Nhis fifth spoonful of sugar,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the taste of the coffee I usually drink\Nspread through my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That stranger enjoyed it as he drank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So I lowered my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it took.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what made me stop killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,For those six months,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.57,0:20:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,why didn't you ask me to teach you\Nhow to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Because…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that\NI shouldn't drag you into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you absolutely have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Rosso.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing someone is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All you need to do\Nis forget the taste of sugar.
